Find the value of [`a`] so that the vector field [`\vec{A}`] below is a magnetic field.

[``\vec{A}=[$b]\ r\ sin(\phi)\ \hat{a_r} + [$c]\ r\ sin(\phi)cot(\theta)\ \hat{a_{\theta}} + a\ r\ cos(\phi)sin(\theta)\ \hat{a_{\phi}}``]

[`a=`] [_____]{"$Ans"} 

